    dc:description "Figure 23. Insectgalls of Parque Nacional da Serra dos Órgãos (RJ,Brazil):(A-J) On Rubiaceae:(A) On Psychotria sp.2, leafgall,(B) On Randia armata (Sw.) DC.,leaf gall,(C-F) On Rudgeajasminoides (Cham) Müll.Arg.:(C) stem gall,(D) stem gall,(E) leafvein gall,(F) leaf gall,(G-H) On Rudgeasp.1, (G) leafgall,(H) leaf gall,(I) On Rudgea sp.2, leafgall,(J) On Rudgea sp.3, leaf gall,(K-L) On Casearia pauciflora Cambess.(Salicaceae):(K) bud gall, (L) leafpetiole gall." ;
